"tag-good-deeds-hasanat","tag-hearts-al-qulub","tag-humility-al-tawadu","tag-knowledge-al-ilm","tag-manners-adab","tag-prayer-al-salat","tag-refuge-al-taawwudh","tag-reverence-al-khushu","tag-satisfaction-al-ridaa","tag-self-al-nafs","tag-supplication-al-dua","tag-welfare-al-maslahah"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-3Dn","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":1060,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/10\/22\/seek-refuge-disability-laziness\/","url_meta":{"origin":13973,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Grant my soul righteousness and purify it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 22, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Arqam reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would supplicate, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in You from disability, sloth, cowardice, miserliness, senility, and the punishment of the grave. O Allah, grant my soul a sense of righteousness and purify it, for You are\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15364,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/24\/seek-refuge-bad-dream-nightmare\/","url_meta":{"origin":13973,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dreams: Refuge in Allah from nightmares","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Qatadah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe good dream is from Allah and the bad dream is from Satan. Whoever sees something he dislikes, let him blow to his left side three times and seek refuge from Satan. Verily, it will not harm him\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18328,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/02\/supplication-dua-morning-evening\/","url_meta":{"origin":13973,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: All praise is due to Allah, morning and evening","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 2, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would say during the evening, \u201cWe have entered the evening and so has the dominion of Allah. All praise is due to Allah, there is no God but Allah alone without any partners.\u201d I think the Prophet said\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34606,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/11\/30\/refuge-from-shaytan-kibr\/","url_meta":{"origin":13973,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Arrogance: The Prophet seeks refuge from Satan\u2019s pride","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 30, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in You from the accursed Satan, his madness, his pride, and his poetry.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 808 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37682,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/01\/26\/refuge-debt-oppression\/","url_meta":{"origin":13973,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Seeking refuge from debt and oppression","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 26, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in You from anxiety, sorrow, disability, laziness, cowardice, miserliness, the burdens of debt, and the repression of men.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6369 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38383,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/10\/24\/prophet-refuge-injustice\/","url_meta":{"origin":13973,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet seeks refuge from committing injustice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 24, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would say, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in You from poverty, scarcity, and humiliation. I seek refuge in You from committing wrong or being wronged.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 1544 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13973","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=13973"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13973\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=13973"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=13973"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=13973"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}